server.js 
<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
> create function and request and response 
>cmd node server.js 
>go to package.json file wipe test add start insted and app.js
>npm start
>p.json dev then server.js but when you run server.js 
>npm run dev server.js
>in node if you want to server restart 
>install npm i -g nodemon 
>p.json just add node insted nodemon to restart server automatically

